<h2>Download Welcome to Freddy's</h2>
<strong>Prepare to take on the night shift at the infamous Freddy Fazbear's Pizza.</strong> Click the download button to start your career as a night guard, where you will face more than just mischievous robots. Keep the doors closed, conserve power, and survive the night - if you can.
<h3>Gameplay Overview</h3>
In Welcome to Freddy's, players must manage their resources effectively to make it through each night:
<ul>
 	<li><strong>Monitor Cameras:</strong> Keep an eye on the animatronic characters through the pizzeria's security cameras.</li>
 	<li><strong>Manage Power:</strong> Use power judiciously to operate cameras, lights, and the two specially mechanized doors that can keep the animatronics at bay.</li>
 	<li><strong>Survive the Night:</strong> Ensure that none of the animatronics make it into your office, as Freddy and his band pose a deadly risk after dark.</li>
</ul>
