<h4>Unique Challenges and Features</h4>
Welcome to Freddy's provides a fresh take on the original FNaF mechanics, introducing new challenges and features:
<ul>
 	<li><strong>Dynamic Animatronics:</strong> Each character has unique patterns and quirks that you must learn to predict and counter.</li>
 	<li><strong>Innovative Power Management:</strong> Balancing the use of cameras, doors, and lights is crucial to maintaining safety and power throughout the night.</li>
 	<li><strong>Engaging Storyline:</strong> Uncover the secrets behind Freddy Fazbear’s Pizza through gameplay and hidden Easter eggs.</li>
</ul>
<h4>System Requirements</h4>
To ensure optimal gameplay experience, your system should meet the following specifications:
<ul>
 	<li><strong>Display:</strong> Widescreen monitor with a minimum resolution of 720p</li>
 	<li><strong>Memory:</strong> At least 2GB of RAM</li>
